s1: ^Kon'nichiwaaa uwu… As you could probably guess, I am into Japan stuff. I watch loads of anime, into manga and some games as well. s2: ^Hi there! I am an ENFP, if you believe in that stuff. I like going out with my mates, getting to know people. s3: ^Heya! I am a laid-back girl looking for like-minded souls to get to know. After a not so nice breakup, I feel like I am ready to try again with the right person. I am slow to trust at first, but once I feel comfortable with a person I climb out of my shell.
s4: ^Welcome 😊 I am a chill and friendly person looking to get to know people here. Well, ofc I am, it is a dating site after all ahah. I like Travelling, food, trying out exotic foods, cocktails.
